Text: Sorry about that had a power down, and it screwed somethings up but up and running again.

To Install The game you must first download and install Daemon-Tools (can be found on this site). Then right click on the quick launch icon for Daemon-Tools, chooose the top option, then the top option again and then "Mount". Now select the Alien VS Predator .CUE file and the installation will start!
